---
/**
 * WhyNow — the regulatory window (homepage-hero-and-usecases.md §3).
 * Sits after the use cases (value → why the window is open). Copper accents
 * carry the regulatory/heritage warmth. HEDGED, fact-checked as of June 2026:
 * GENIUS Act = signed into law (2025); CLARITY Act = advancing, not yet law.
 * Copy and the "not legal advice" disclaimer are verbatim from the source doc.
 */
import Eyebrow from './Eyebrow.astro';
import Button from './Button.astro';
---

<section class="section why-now">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <Eyebrow variant="copper">Why now</Eyebrow>
      <h2>For years the blocker wasn't the technology. It was the rules.</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        That's changing fast. A federal stablecoin law is on the books, market-structure rules are
        advancing, and the institutions that move now will be ready when they land.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2 whynow-grid grid">
      <article class="card whynow-card">
        <div class="whynow-card__head">
          <span class="whynow-card__name">GENIUS Act</span>
          <span class="whynow-card__badge whynow-card__badge--law">Signed into law · 2025</span>
        </div>
        <p class="whynow-card__body">
          The first federal framework for payment stablecoins. It turns stablecoin settlement from a
          gray area into a sanctioned rail enterprises can build on. Rulemaking is still rolling
          out.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card whynow-card">
        <div class="whynow-card__head">
          <span class="whynow-card__name">CLARITY Act</span>
          <span class="whynow-card__badge whynow-card__badge--pending">Advancing · not yet law</span
          >
        </div>
        <p class="whynow-card__body">
          Market-structure legislation that would reduce the "is it a security?" risk stalling
          tokenization. Cleared the Senate Banking Committee in May 2026; a full Senate vote
          remains.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="whynow-foot">
      <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" arrow>Start the conversation</Button>
      <p class="whynow-disclaimer">
        Regulatory status as of June 2026. Directional, not legal advice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
